---+ Change password

   * Go to [[https://wiki.ukp.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de/pwchange/index.pl][password change webpage]]
   * If you workstation is in the UKP domain, simply use the =passwd= command on the command line
   * Alternatively log in via ssh to any of our compute servers and use =passwd= on the command line there
